	<tr>
	<td width=390 valign=top>
		
		<center>
		<p>
		<b><a href="/index.html">Home</a>  |  <a href="/departments/departments.html">Departments</a>  |  <a href="/search/query.html">Search</a>  |  <a href="/forums/index.html">Message Boards</a></b>
		<pre>
		</pre>
				<font size=5><b></b></font><br>
				<font size=6><b>97/02-Personal Adviser:  It All Adds Up</b></font><br>
				<font size=4></font><p>
				</center>
				
				<blockquote>
					<center>
						<font size=4><b><i></i></b></font><p>
					</center>
					<font size=4>
						By Reshma Memon Yaqub<p>
Hardware stores
Computer makers sell used, refurbished, and excess computers at 
20 to 50 percent off at factory-outlet stores. Most of the computers are from 30-day customer returns to retail stores, and there's nothing wrong with them. Any broken machines have been fixed. For current inventories, call Compaq (800-318-6919), IBM (800-426-7015), Dell (800-336-2891), or Micron (800-964-2766, ext. 6363).<p>
Policy Previews
Insurance Information (800-472-5800) will search its database of 600 companies for the five cheapest term-life-insurance policies. The charge: $50. SelectQuote (800-343-1985) offers a free report based on the 18 companies it represents, and Quotesmith (800-431-1147) provides a free comparison of the 140 companies that pay to be on its list.<p>
The Play's the Thing
You purchased those theater tickets ages ago; now you have to go out of town. Good thing you bought ticket insurance from Theatre Direct (212-541-8457). For five dollars per ticket, you can return Broadway and Off Broadway tickets for a full refund two business days before the show. <p>
Fully Furnished
Buy furniture, fixtures, wallpaper, and carpeting straight from manufacturers. The Fine Furniture and Furnishings Discount Shopping Guide ($14.95, 810-644-3440) lists the phone numbers of more than 200 manufacturers that ship directly to your door. A good place to start: Hickory Furniture Mart (800-462-MART), a 17-acre mall with 65 showrooms. <p>
Cheap Reads 
Get magazines at below-normal prices: Delta Publishing (800-736-3547) and Below Wholesale Magazines (800-800-0062) supply magazines to doctors' and dentists' waiting rooms, but they accept orders from anyone.<p>
KEYWORDS:
deal, bargain, discount

					</font>
					<p>
		
		
		
