<font size=+1><b>Company Index</b><br>
</font>						<a href="#NASD:YELL">Yellow Corporation</a><br>

						<a href="#NYSE:MER">Merrill Lynch & Co., Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:AIND">Arnold Industries, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:ODFL">Old Dominion Freight Line, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:SWFT">Swift Transportation Co., Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:WERN">Werner Enterprises, Inc.</a><br>

						<a href="#NASD:LSTR">Landstar System, Inc.</a><br>

